attributes.name: Ashen Tiger
attributes.description: Neither light nor color can escape the deep darkness of its fur. But do you know what can? Love! And this big kitty needs lots of it.

attributes.name: Barkimedes' Puppy
attributes.description: The grown spawn of the great Barkimedes and a settlement Mastiff; a forbidden romance for the ages.

attributes.name: Chromal Tiger
attributes.description: The very essence of light and color dwells within each strand of fur of this tiger. And they deserve scritches behind their ears. Yes they do! Yes they do.

attributes.name: Galaxy Rabbit
attributes.description: Brimming with awe, the vast expanse of the universe resides within the fur of this rabbit. And if you pet them, you might just feel it too.

attributes.name: Goldfish in Porcelain Bowl
attributes.description: Feel free to admire, but watch out; this feisty goldfish loves to splash anyone who comes in range.
